---
title: Hearty Double Beef and Black Bean Chili with Mexican-Spiced Sweet Potatoes
description: We're giving chili night an upgrade with Mexican-seasoned sweet potatoes, smoky beef and hearty beans! A dollop of sour cream and a sprinkle of cheese finish each bowl with a fresh and creamy touch.
